
Competencies

Rails is a web app framework for Ruby that packages many common application functions “out the box” so developers do not have to spend time on it
This way, you can actually get a rails app up and running quite quickly
Rails is very “opinionated”, there is a “right” way to do things in Rails as opposed to Sinatra
Rails has great documentation thanks to a robust and active community, it would behoove you to take advantage

